  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="purpose-leccion-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>The purpose of this lesson is for students to make sense of line plots that represent measurements to the nearest half or fourth of an inch.</p>
  </paragraphs>

